text: Sokolica may refer to: *Sokolica, Lower Silesian Voivodeship (south-west Poland) *Sokolica, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship (north Poland) *Sokolica (Pieniny), peak in Pieniny, mountain range in the south of Poland. *Sokolica Monastery, a Serbian Orthodox monastery in Kosovo *Sokolica (mountain), a Mountain in Kosovo
title: Sokolica
